OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with murder
OL,4,Cof Teesside woman in 2000
OL,6,FA 65-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe death of Teesside woman Vicky
OL,9,FGlass in 2000.
OL,11,FThe man was arrested in the Lancashire
OL,12,Farea on Friday morning (12 June).
OL,14,FHe remains in police custody in
OL,15,FLancashire, where he will be
OL,16,Finterviewed by Cleveland Police
OL,17,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/2
