CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781719875
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with murder
OL,4,Cof Teesside woman in 2000
OL,6,F21-year-old Vicky was last seen at
OL,7,Faround 4am on 24 September 2000 as she
OL,8,Fgot out of a taxi in the Union Street
OL,9,Farea of Middlesbrough.
OL,11,FA few weeks later, on 3rd November
OL,12,F2000, Vicky's body was discovered in a
OL,13,Fstream in the village of Danby in the
OL,14,FNorth York Moors.
OL,16,FPolice then launched a murder
OL,17,Finvestigation, over the years a number
OL,18,Fof people have been arrested and
OL,19,Fadditional people were interviewed,
OL,20,Fbut no-one has ever been charged with
OL,21,FVicky's murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/2
